        bit bucket has all the repositories 
        copilot (LLM model)would helps to give the predictions like whats the error, which repo gets to commit, which team can responsible for that
           issue. those details we can get it only when we integrate the LLM model (AI) with the tools(bit bucket). here the MCP server helps to 
